item.title: Help asap ;)
item.dc:creator: @Clawz_fury lare69
item.description:
@Clawz_fury wrote:

[quote=“Abandoned Dreams, post:3, topic:375971”][quote author=DivineSouls link=topic=471905.msg3451177#msg3451177 date=1293757934]
What do you want to unblock from your ISP? There isn’t really any reason to have a 2nd world, in less you are having trouble processing all the players on a single server. Sure you can have two worlds. I kind of doubt you are the owner of Near Reality or something, so there isn’t much of a point.
[/quote]I Want To Unblock Port 43594 or 5555 From My ISP.
And I Want A 2nd World Because Well, My Idea. How Can I Make A 2nd World?[/quote]

Height level 4 is duplicate world ;), so is 8, 12, 16, 20 etc. So just change your height level to 4.

Read full topic
